---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="Welcome to DGTS">
  <div class="page-main">
    <section class="space-y-6 py-12 sm:py-20 lg:py-20">
      <div
        class="container flex max-w-5xl flex-col items-center gap-5 text-center"
      >
        <h1
          class="text-balance font-heading text-4xl sm:text-2xl md:text-4xl lg:text-[42px]"
          style="width: 80%;"
        >
          <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">
            <font style="vertical-align: inherit;"
              >吾生也有涯,而知也无涯,以有涯随无涯,殆已</font
            >
          </font>
        </h1>

        <p
          class="max-w-2xl text-balance leading-normal text-muted-foreground sm:text-xs sm:leading-8"
        >
          <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">
            <font style="vertical-align: inherit;"
              >天下间的知识如浩瀚大海，无穷无尽，但人的时间、精力、心思却有限。如果盲目追求，没有目标和方向，就真的没完没了；但如果所学习的是真知和正见，确定自己的目标，有的放矢地去学习，而不是盲目追求知识，就是值得鼓励和欣赏的。</font
            >
          </font>
        </p>

      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<!-- 吾生也有涯,而知也无涯,以有涯随无涯,殆已 -->
<!-- 天下间的知识如浩瀚大海，无穷无尽，但人的时间、精力、心思却有限。如果盲目追求，没有目标和方向，就真的没完没了；但如果所学习的是真知和正见，确定自己的目标，有的放矢地去学习，而不是盲目追求知识，就是值得鼓励和欣赏的。 -->

<style lang="less">
  .section.connector_hero {
    background-color: var(--base-color-brand--yellow-light);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .spray-bg-container {
    z-index: 0;
    opacity: 0.6;
    pointer-events: none;
    mix-blend-mode: multiply;
    background-image: url('/assets/images/page/home/cartoon_logo_cover.png');
    background-position: 50%;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-size: cover;
    background-attachment: scroll;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0%;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .connectors-hero-graphic-container {
    pointer-events: none;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: flex-end;
    height: 220px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .w-layout-hflex {
    flex-direction: row;
    align-items: flex-start;
    display: flex;
  }

  .connectors-hero-graphic {
    width: 110%;
    max-width: none;
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
  }
</style>
